>\n不過家間公司就feel到點都唔會fd到"},{"pid":"b90473923bbaf01ed06a8763ff31239ad016ef9e","tid":2218953,"uid":63440,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"第一份工既同事都差唔多年紀<br />\n所以都做到fd 試過出黎bbq行山食飯<br />\n但之後兩份工就覺得唔好搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食飯都情願自己一個食 比返少少食飯私人時間自己好過"},{"pid":"662eef7a5b06fbadcea3e4ffc37e0f741c9b92fa","tid":2218953,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66cdf4feacf7d33ddbcfbf1e289e8d8beed5a331","tid":2218953,"uid":89240,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"最好唔好，過來人<br />\n由其香噴噴果d靚女<br />\n全部有毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"之有個靚女唔係咩高層又好煩膠<br />\n但心腸幾好,請晒低層食飯 <br />\nOA 茶水姐姐 十卜狗都有份<br />\n不過依家都無聯絡"},{"pid":"0999ad973000a6a3f2df06736c314886cf08ecc9","tid":2218953,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"86b4acaca27753970cf359120aa26a05be66c2bc","tid":2218953,"uid":123308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"如果喺另一平行時空，<br />\n你同你同事唔係同事，咁會唔會做朋友？<br />\n「同事」二字就限制一切？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過現實中，的確有難度<br />\n只能夠講萬事小心"},{"pid":"e37d8a4eec74cf98f6b6d36485dfe27f2047171c","tid":2218953,"uid":215087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"離職後咪可以囉"},{"pid":"6f5788b3c7e396cfa2aceb3c49cfb77692796304","tid":2218953,"uid":325263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66cdf4feacf7d33ddbcfbf1e289e8d8beed5a331","tid":2218953,"uid":89240,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"最好唔好，過來人<br />\n由其香噴噴果d靚女<br />\n全部有毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:29:07.000Z","msg":"More details"},{"pid":"c12cd5ba66818990f658e833b8ec8761c0f00d92","tid":2218953,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:56:43.000Z","ms